{"tid":2458404,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"來自課長們的貢獻 《原神》母公司米哈遊中國新總部超氣派","createTime":"2021-03-23T11:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T02:49:07.000Z","uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"36ae5a847c8a6c56e013e25f1bdfdf6b11dc2f53","tid":2458404,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/47094/mihoyo-new-office\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F47094%2Fmihoyo-new-office&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97QwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=74d6d4a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/47094/mihoyo-new-office</a><br />\n<br />\n《原神》開發商 miHoYo（米哈遊）近幾年來可說是賺很大，其位於中國的新總部大樓外觀和內部格局被日本網友上傳到了推特，引發外界關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Kou_Kun94/status/1368471101576081408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKou_Kun94%2Fstatus%2F1368471101576081408&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97QwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=081305fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKou_Kun94%2Fstatus%2F1368471101576081408&h=9bf15904\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Kou_Kun94/status/1368471101576081408</a><br />\n<br />\n受惠於《原神》推出後在全球大放異彩，直接盤據各地的暢銷排行榜，光是《原神》在手機平台的月收入 1.75 億美元（約新台幣 49 億元），是近期全球最高收入手遊。<br />\n<br />\n而米哈遊的總部位於上海。上海算是一個物價並不便宜的地區，米哈遊能在寸土寸金的上海落成新的一棟辦公大樓，確實家底深厚。"},{"pid":"f029a4a9ac3f5e87e6ef61a22fa01dfefb1b67ad","tid":2458404,"uid":66087,"like":81,"dislike":4,"score":77,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:38:43.000Z","msg":"一個二個養到大陸跨國公司肥肥白白<br />\n<br />\n邊個再課金死全家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19599121250e19539abacdb57cb6417e595976c6","tid":2458404,"uid":276865,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"f029a4a9ac3f5e87e6ef61a22fa01dfefb1b67ad","tid":2458404,"uid":66087,"like":81,"dislike":4,"score":77,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:38:43.00