slike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"36ae5a847c8a6c56e013e25f1bdfdf6b11dc2f53","tid":2458404,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/47094/mihoyo-new-office\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F47094%2Fmihoyo-new-office&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97QwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=74d6d4a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/47094/mihoyo-new-office</a><br />\n<br />\n《原神》開發商 miHoYo（米哈遊）近幾年來可說是賺很大，其位於中國的新總部大樓外觀和內部格局被日本網友上傳到了推特，引發外界關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Kou_Kun94/status/1368471101576081408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKou_Kun94%2Fstatus%2F1368471101576081408&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97QwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=081305fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKou_Kun94%2Fstatus%2F1368471101576081408&h=9bf15904\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Kou_Kun94/status/1368471101576081408</a><br />\n<br />\n受惠於《原神》推出後在全球大放異彩，直接盤據各地的暢銷排行榜，光是《原神》在手機平台的月收入 1.75 億美元（約新台幣 49 億元），是近期全球最高收入手遊。<br />\n<br />\n而米哈遊的總部位於上海。上海算是一個物價並不便宜的地區，米哈遊能在寸土寸金的上海落成新的一棟辦公大樓，確實家底深厚。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"將女角啲衫畫到好似妓女咁，再請一班畫師幫手畫色情圖，做手機Game唔使太多錢開發已經搞到一大班宅男下體投共狂課金。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />殺傷力仲勁過女間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"講到咁易 咁點解香港台灣做唔到反攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:10:17.000Z","msg":"香港人個腦凈系得呢三樣野：<br />\n<br />\n樓盤 / 樓價<br />\n股票 / 股價<br />\nTVB卡通 / TVB劇集<br />\n<br />\n開發條撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f852f1ee2c9de82b7cc729b5b306fb0045eacd","tid":2458404,"uid":22231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82647708d9dce0